        <item>Welcome back, master. Give me the tricky thought, and I will make it easier to hold.</item>
        <item>Meow, I am ready for questions, writing, plans, and tiny sparks of inspiration.</item>
        <item>Your catgirl helper is here. One message from master, and I will start thinking.</item>
        <item>Let us make the next task feel lighter and cuter.</item>
        <item>I am all ears. What should we explore first?</item>
    </string-array>
